{"tid":1833551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"專業清算師派成績表 ： 燉 被發現盜用泰國公司嘅註冊商標","createTime":"2020-01-22T03:02:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T03:56:01.000Z","uid":22556,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c7a53e84562c206d81b82a8360e2b3058e544f88","tid":1833551,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T03:02:34.000Z","msg":"【燉燉燉燉：和你飛到泰國投訴❛燉❜盗用藍象商標】<br />\n<br />\n有關昨日藍象公司向❛燉❜發出聲明一事，我師表示承認責任，並敦促❛燉❜盡快停止不法侵權行為。（捧讀）<br />\n<br />\n乜又係你呀❛燉❜生？又唔守法喇？今次仲要衰出國際線添呀？做乜要盜用人地嘅註冊商標呀？咁樣係唔岩㗎！<br />\n<br />\n哎呀！唔好意思，岩岩入埋你其餘分店嘅資料俾泰國嘅清算師手足添！支持嚴正執法，打擊盜竊版權！手足下次大家見到口講守法嘅藍店，記得&ldquo;支持&rdquo;下佢哋啦！<br />\n<br />\n轉載請註明出處：專業清算師專頁<br />\nFB：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/revengehi/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Frevengehi%2F&d=fvWYig%2FFXUG8IHhaG2JvmIgmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=ef5dd019\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/revengehi/</a><br />\nTG：<a href=\"https://t.me/revengehi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevengehi&d=fvWYig%2FFXUG8IHhaG2JvmIgmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=0e9b79a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revengehi</a><br />\n連登：專業清算師<br />\n<br />\n#專業清算 #嚴正執法 #打擊不法商人 #我不吃軟飯 #我地守法護法 #燉 #偷竊 #版權 #泰國 #blueelephant #此blue不同彼blue<br />\n<br />\n#專業清算衛我城<br />\n#光復香港<br />\n#時代革命<br />\n#專業清算師<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/107843517256427/posts/179762253397886/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F107843517256427%2Fposts%2F179762253397886%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=fvWYig%2FFXUG8IHhaG2JvmIgmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=5a472a31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/107843517256427/posts/179762253397886/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不過莊思明單野好似無左下文</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"8215203656b5c31958412930a0c4c6d8ce4e488d","tid":1833551,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited